The residuals pass the ADF test of stationarity with a p-value of 0.08, but not the Box-Ljung test of independence up to 24 lags. Its ACF and PACF suggests a much weaker ARMA effects, if none.

2. Forecast

This time, the forecast’s trend lies above the actual, not as good as the best model.

The test set residuals don’t pass the ADF test of stationarity, nor the Box-Ljung test of independence up to 24 lags. Its ACF and PACF suggests some AR effects.
